_nehemiah_11_10","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":17,"bookName":"Nehemiah","bookAbbrev":"nehemiah","chapter":11,"verse":10,"text":"Of the priests: both Jadia son of Joarib, and Jachin.","searchKeywords":["the","priests","both","jadia","son","joarib","and","jachin"]},{"verseId":"brenton_nehemiah_11_11","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":17,"bookName":"Nehemiah","bookAbbrev":"nehemiah","chapter":11,"verse":11,"text":"Saraia, son of Elchia, son of Mesulam, son of Sadduc, son of Marioth, son of Aetoth, was over the house of God.","searchKeywords":["saraia","son","elchia","mesulam","sadduc","marioth","aetoth","was","over","the","house","god"]},{"verseId":"brenton_nehemiah_11_12","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":17,"bookName":"Nehemiah","bookAbbrev":"nehemiah","chapter":11,"verse":12,"text":"And their brethren doing the work of the house were eight hundred and twenty-two: and Adaia son of Jeroam, son of Phalalia, son of Amasi, son of Zacharia, son of Phassur, son of Melchia,","searchKeywords":["and","their","brethren","doing","the","work","house","were","eight","hundred","twenty","two","adaia","son","jeroam","phalalia","amasi","zacharia","phassur","melchia"]},{"verseId":"brenton_nehemiah_11_13","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":17,"bookName":"Nehemiah","bookAbbrev":"nehemiah","chapter":11,"verse":13,"text":"and his brethren, chiefs of families, two hundred and forty-two: and Amasia son of Esdriel, son of Mesarimith, son of Emmer,","searchKeywords":["and","his","brethren","chiefs","families","two","hundred","forty","amasia","son","esdriel","mesarimith","emmer"]},{"verseId":"brenton_nehemiah_11_14","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":17,"bookName":"Nehemiah","bookAbbrev":"nehemiah","chapter":11,"verse":14,"text":"and his brethren, mighty men of war, a hundred and twenty-eight: and overseer Badiel son of great men.","searchKeywords":["and","his","brethren","mighty","men","